# 🔐 HOW TO GET WHATSAPP CREDENTIALS:
# 1. Go to: https://developers.facebook.com/apps
# 2. Create/Select your WhatsApp Business App
# 3. Navigate to WhatsApp > API Setup
# 4. Copy: Temporary Access Token, Phone Number ID
# 5. Set your own VERIFY_TOKEN (any unique string)
# 6. Configure webhook URL: https://your-vercel-domain.vercel.app/webhook
